data.description: Welcome home to 134 Fern Lane!  This cute and cozy home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 baths with split and open floor plan.  You'll fall in love with the space that the open living, kitchen and dining combination has to offer.  Tastefully enhanced with new floors, drywall, paint, ceiling fixtures, roof and more!   Whole AC unit and de-humidifier installed in 2019.  Spacious chain link fenced yard with rear vehicle access.  Flood Zone X.  Detached shed to remain, but detached dog grooming building to be removed prior to act of sale.  NEW PRICE & Seller will pay up to $1,500.00 towards Buyer's closing cost with an acceptable offer!  WHAT A DEAL!
